import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
s = sys.stdin.readline().strip()

ans = []

for i in range(n):
    if s[i] == '[':
        ans.append('+')
        ans.append('-')
    else:
        ans.append('|')
        ans.append('+')
        ans.append('-')
        ans.append('|')

print(''.join(ans))

def main():
    n = int(input())
    brackets = input()
    brackets = brackets.replace('[', '|+-')
    brackets = brackets.replace(']', '-+|')
    print(brackets)


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
